title: Project Plan - IntentText Feature Demo
summary: Comprehensive plan demonstrating IntentText features: Query, Schema, Templates, Themes, Trust, and Index.

section: Overview
note: This document demonstrates the core features of IntentText
sub: Key Features
- Query Language for filtering documents
- Schema Validation for structured data
- Templates with {{variable}} merging
- Trust system with seal, sign, and verify
- Index builder for multi-document queries
- Theme system for styled rendering

