section: Trust System Demo
note: Documents can be sealed, signed, and verified
sub: Workflow
1. Write your document
2. Seal it with `cli.js seal` — adds freeze: and sign: blocks
3. Verify with `cli.js verify` — confirms integrity via SHA-256 hash

sub: Amendment Support
note: Frozen documents can be amended with amendment: blocks
text: Amendments are excluded from the integrity hash, so the seal remains valid

section: Index and Multi-Document Query Demo
note: Build indexes across folders for cross-document queries
sub: Index Commands
text: `cli.js index <dir>` builds a .it-index file
text: `cli.js query <dir> --type task` queries across all .it files

